45
00:01:29,706 --> 00:01:32,657
what made it feel right for Arlo.

46
00:01:32,657 --> 00:01:34,686
First of all, there was a series of cells

47
00:01:34,686 --> 00:01:36,870
that formed the main feature of the pattern.

48
00:01:36,870 --> 00:01:38,697
In terms of color, these cells

49
00:01:38,697 --> 00:01:40,843
