53
00:01:48,764 --> 00:01:51,423
Finally, the cells that made up the main pattern

54
00:01:51,423 --> 00:01:54,947
were displaced from the surface, so it was kind of bumpy.

55
00:01:54,947 --> 00:01:57,256
